node.text: The Knicks are preparing to land both Damian Lillard and Zion Williamson during this upcoming season. With both superstars being upset at their organization and undecided on their decision to return, New York’s front office is looking to take advantage of the opportunity and welcome two of the hottest superstars in the league to Madison Square Garden. Follow @mocktrades to see the projected mock trades that’ll form the newest superstar duo in New York.
